{"tid":668801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又有紅van超載　59歲司機被捕","createTime":"2018-05-18T02:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T03:11:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b07a2d8c985b32ab930369ed1dffb62a31383a8b","tid":668801,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T02:41:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180518/20394456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F20394456&d=4RKMSrBp3%2BDoZuM3FwVM1gRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=e7f28dfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F20394456&h=0204f3af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180518/20394456</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月18日 <br />\n<br />\n又有紅van超載　59歲司機被捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180518/large/18la6p21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180518%2Flarge%2F18la6p21.jpg&h=69569ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■昨被發現超載的小巴違法加裝座位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方連續第二日嚴厲打擊新界區小巴超載問題，昨凌晨於大埔再拘捕一名涉嫌超載小巴司機。而行走元朗與大棠路線，有小巴因違法加裝座位及增設「企位」超載等，包括一名71歲女司機共3名司機被拘捕後，《蘋果》昨日凌晨乘搭同一條線，未發現超載情況，疑風頭火勢下司機暫時收斂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方新界北總區交通部特遣隊，連續第二日打擊區內小巴超載，昨晨5時於大埔太和路截查一輛涉嫌超載的小巴，並以涉嫌危險駕駛拘捕姓林（59歲）小巴司機。現場消息指，該輛16座紅色小巴，客滿後由元朗開往大埔，駛至林村附近讓一名女子及一名女童登車。警方尾隨並於太湖花園外避車處將小巴截停作檢控。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180518/large/18la6p22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180518%2Flarge%2F18la6p22.jpg&h=e7d99818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■來往大棠至元朗的小巴超載情況嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沿途不斷有人截車<br />\n<br />\n而來往大棠路黃泥墩至元朗市中心的紅色小巴，由於車少人多，超載情況嚴重。警方於前日採取突擊行動，截獲3輛超載小巴，其中一輛19座小巴超載至25人，包括4個「企位」，拘捕3名司機，包括一名年屆71歲的女司機。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》昨清晨5時於黃泥墩上車，發現小巴司機位旁未有加設座位，總站上車只有3、4名乘客，途中陸續有人上車，行了一半路程已經全車客滿。其間路邊均有多名市民截車，懷疑風頭火勢下，司機都耍手不敢停車。記者其後再坐另一程車折返，於大棠村上車，同樣行至一半便客滿，沒發現超載情況。<br />\n<br />\n■記者潘婉玲  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n鄰居變刀賊入屋綁劫獨居婦　警搜捕一日後拉人<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n涉不良營商　健身中心6人被捕"},{"pid":"5461e706bdc48a5c70b8058c12f31ea5564f7e4e","tid":668801,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T02:55:38.000Z","msg":"25人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d5375ac3c2776d82a432dfb818910ffd831110","tid":668801,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5461e706bdc48a5c70b8058c12f31ea5564f7e4e","tid":668801,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T02:55:38.000Z","msg":"25人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:02:51.000Z","msg":"歡樂滿東華"},{"pid":"570871962a780671171c9c38373a3e6d77854252","tid":668801,"uid":65686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:05:28.000Z","msg":"年屆71歲的女司機"},{"pid":"209172475299cd246872fb995c0236f14b89cbf6","tid":668801,"uid":35468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:06:43.000Z","msg":"71歲女司機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce9266bc641ae45016e070a309534b2c5cb5188","tid":668801,"uid":2959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:08:44.000Z","msg":"小巴企位真係好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efccade0483cb0ea72aa0954b0ae3d52303342a5","tid":668801,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:11:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>71歲女司機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係嚇左嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}